com.interpss.simu.multicase.aclf

Interface AclfMultiStudyCase

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, MultiStudyCase, NameTag, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ContingencyAnalysis, DStabMultiStudyCase
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AclfMultiStudyCaseImpl, ContingencyAnalysisImpl, DStabMultiStudyCaseImpl

    public interface AclfMultiStudyCase
extends MultiStudyCase
    A representation of the model object 'Aclf Multi Study Case'. multi study case for AclfNet related analysis, such as contingey analysis.

    The following features are supported:

    • Remote Job Creation
    • Lf Tolerance
    • Bus Voltage Upper Limit PU
    • Bus Voltage Lower Limit PU
    • Aclf Grid Option
    • Bus Result Summary
    • Branch Result Summary
    See Also:
    MCaseAclfPackage.getAclfMultiStudyCase()
